data.meta_description:
8,519 likes, 410 comments - realbillduke on February 2, 2024: "I was deeply saddened to hear about the passing of Carl Weathers. He was a remarkable individual who touched the lives of many. Carl's warmth, kindness and tremendous talent will always be remembered by those who had the privilege of knowing and working with him. While words may offer little solace in moments like these, please know that Carl and his family are in my thoughts and prayers.

May the Weathers family find comfort in the love and support of friends and other family members as you navigate through this period of mourning. Wishing you strength, peace and blessings in the days ahead - Bill Duke

#Predator #Rocky #ApolloCreed #TheMandalorian #ActionJackson #HappyGilmore #realBillDuke #ArrestedDevelopment #NewOrleans #FootballPlayer #actor #CarlWeathers #coribanks444".
